title: 160: Could 49ers trade for Kirk Cousins? Combined mock draft
itunes:title: 160: Could 49ers trade for Kirk Cousins? Combined mock draft
description:
Could the San Francisco 49ers give up the 2nd overall pick in the draft and trade for quarterback Kirk Cousins? Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks discuss how teams looking for QBs approach the draft and free agency. DJ and Bucky also combine to make every first round pick in a new mock draft.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
